author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Great stream today, another adventure at enderworld.
The stream again had a good BGM selection. :_ハート:

I hope Rushia-daitenshi will forgive me, I didn't enjoy this stream due to several headaches at night and having noticed about early scheduling (According to Twitter, the stream was scheduled to 6:00 p.m., but due to a date with the otolaryngologist, it had re-scheduled to 1:30 p.m.)
I was watching it, but several times I started to falling asleep in fact of healing. :_あせり:

And the adventure were the remains of the Minecraft Olympics and the second Enderworld adventure... This time was farming until dying against the endermen. :_ドクロ:
Later, a return... The Usagi trade center (Finally Pekora-san's house was a trade stand) and a happy ending with the Fandead Joseph. (I couldn't understand how Joseph was healed) :_るんるん:

Again the crashes were the partypoopers of the day. They Didn't leave to enjoy and sometimes I fell asleep with the headache. :_おこなのです: :_どんっ: :_どんっ:

At least I could enjoy the Supaachaato Orei Time, but with short time. :_しょぼん:
